trans-unit.source: The exception that is thrown when an operation is performed on a disposed object.
trans-unit.target: 对已释放的对象执行操作时所引发的异常。

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.ObjectDisposedException> is thrown when you try to access a member of an object that implements the <xref:System.IDisposable> interface, and that object has been disposed.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ObjectDisposedException>你尝试访问实现的对象的成员时，将引发<xref:System.IDisposable>接口，并且该对象已被释放。

trans-unit.source: Typically, this exception is caused by one of the following conditions:
trans-unit.target: 通常情况下，此异常由以下条件之一引起：

trans-unit.source: You've called an object's `Dispose` method, and you’re trying to access an instance member that gets or sets the object's state.
trans-unit.target: 已调用对象的`Dispose`方法，并且你正在尝试访问的实例成员，获取或设置对象的状态。

trans-unit.source: The following example illustrates the <xref:System.ObjectDisposedException> that is thrown when you try to reset the frequency of timer notifications after you call the <xref:System.Threading.Timer.Dispose%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示<xref:System.ObjectDisposedException>当你尝试重置计时器通知的频率之后你调用, 时引发<xref:System.Threading.Timer.Dispose%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法。

trans-unit.source: You've called an object's `Close` method, and you’re trying to access an instance member that gets or sets the object's state.
trans-unit.target: 已调用对象的`Close`方法，并且你正在尝试访问的实例成员，获取或设置对象的状态。

trans-unit.source: Often, the `Close` method provides a type's public implementation of the <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method.
trans-unit.target: 通常情况下，`Close`方法提供类型的公共实现<xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法。

trans-unit.source: You've called an object's `Dispose` method multiple times.
trans-unit.target: 已调用对象的`Dispose`方法多次。

trans-unit.source: Typically, this doesn’t throw an exception.
trans-unit.target: 通常情况下，这不会引发异常。

trans-unit.source: However, depending on how a type implements <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, it may not allow multiple calls to `Dispose`.
trans-unit.target: 但是，根据如何实现一种类型<xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>，它可能不允许对多个调用`Dispose`。

trans-unit.source: In most cases, this exception results from developer error.
trans-unit.target: 在大多数情况下，此异常导致的开发人员错误。

trans-unit.source: Instead of handling the error in a `try`/`catch` block, you should correct the error, typically by reinstantiating the object.
trans-unit.target: 而不是处理中的错误`try` / `catch`块中，你应通过 reinstantiating 对象通常更正该错误。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates an error that causes the `ObjectDisposedException` exception to be thrown.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示了将导致一个错误`ObjectDisposedException`引发异常。

trans-unit.source: This code produces the following output:
trans-unit.target: 此代码生成以下输出：

trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.ObjectDisposedException" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: A string containing the name of the disposed object.
trans-unit.target: 包含已释放对象的名称的字符串。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ObjectDisposedException.Message%2A> property is initialized to a system-supplied message that describes the error and includes the `objectName` parameter.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ObjectDisposedException.Message%2A>属性初始化为系统提供的消息描述错误并包括`objectName`参数。

trans-unit.target: `InnerException`属性的新实例初始化为`null`。

trans-unit.source: If `objectName` is `null`, the `Message` property contains only an error message.
trans-unit.target: 如果`objectName`是`null`、`Message`属性包含仅错误消息。

trans-unit.target: 使用指定的错误消息和对作为此异常原因的内部异常的引用来初始化 <see cref="T:System.ObjectDisposedException" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: An exception that is thrown as a direct result of a previous exception should include a reference to the previous exception in the <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 因前一个异常而直接引发的异常应在 <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> 属性中包含对前一个异常的引用。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property returns the same value that is passed into the constructor.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>属性返回传递到构造函数的相同值。

trans-unit.target: 使用参数名和附加异常信息检索 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> 对象。
